text: Bakeyevo () is a rural locality (a selo) and the administrative center of Bakeyevsky Selsoviet, Sterlibashevsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 507 as of 2010. There are 6 streets. == Geography == It is located 12 km from Sterlibashevo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Sterlibashevsky District
title: Bakeyevo, Sterlibashevsky District, Republic of Bashkortostan
